				<div class="col-md-9">
					<h4> Lion T-Shirt </h4>
					<p> Beautiful, majestic King. He rules with grace, even when we cannot
						fathom the depths of His grace. He is powerful and strong. When He roars,
						the Earth trembles at His might. He is gentle. His heart longs for intimacy
						with His people. He is the Lion of Judah, whose kingship was demonstrated
						through His conquering of sin and death at the cross. The Lion. The Lamb
						who was slain, so that we may spend eternity with Him. He gives boldness
						to those who believe in Him, that they may have courage to overcome,
						saying “Fear not, for I am with you.” He has absolute dominion and rules
						the heavens and the earth. He has created a kingdom, and has called us
						to be co-heirs with Christ. He is the King of Glory, worthy to be praised.
						Holy, righteous, and bold. </p>
				</div>
